<item>
            <title>[SYNAPSE-84] Synapse looses attachment simply routing a message</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-84</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Client send a message with attachment (see TCPMon Screenshot):&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Synapse route it with this simple configuration:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;----- Synapse.xml ------&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;synapse xmlns=&quot;http://ws.apache.org/ns/synapse&quot;&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
     &amp;lt;rules&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;in&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
               &amp;lt;send&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                        &amp;lt;endpoint address=&quot;http://localhost:9999/SincronoAttachment/SincronoAttachment&quot;/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
                &amp;lt;/send&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;drop/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;/in&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;out&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
            &amp;lt;send/&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
        &amp;lt;/out&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    &amp;lt;/rules&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&amp;lt;/synapse&amp;gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;----- End of synapse.xml ------&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Synapse route message to server, but seems attachments are cutted away... (See TCPMon screenshot)&lt;/p&gt;





